---
title: Dukkah Prawn Jumble
description: Looking for a simple showstopper you can rustle together in just twenty minutes? Look no further. The Egyptian blend of dukkah is no ordinary spice mix, which is exactly why it’s the hero ingredient in tonight’s recipe. A crunchy mix of roasted hazelnut, sesame and thyme, we’ve used dukkah to season this prawn and veggie jumble  which works beautifully with fluffy couscous. We think you’ll agree that Chef Lizzie has outdone herself with this recipe!
